{"tid":2071324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蕭生：中共不退讓，26-27號將表決《國安法》！","createTime":"2020-06-19T17:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:28:57.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"19fba501bd141e807b5d3df2f7115d6b5c8fd0d6","tid":2071324,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CBOHA5yBLWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCBOHA5yBLWQ&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=1564ae3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CBOHA5yBLWQ</a><br />\n<br />\n蕭生：<br />\n<br />\n而家有兩個可能性：<br />\n<br />\n一：20/6可能係通過決議，諮詢港人意見，之後再修改法例，到26-27號再開會審議後表決。<br />\n<br />\n二：20/6表決<br />\n<br />\nCable 前幾日講解過中國立法程序：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mkDGLxTlbEE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmkDGLxTlbEE&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=228faf46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mkDGLxTlbEE</a><br />\n<br />\nNow 政情：<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】港區國安法提上人大常委會，但草案內容及立法時間表，外界都所知不多。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委會提早在六月中開會，但起初的議程並無國安法，令外界一度誤以為立法步伐放緩，但北京在人大常委會開會首日，加插港區國安法議程。有建制派對此不感詫異，認為若非為了國安法，何必提早開會。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委會一共開三日會議，星期六早上閉幕，但無公布港區國安法會否即日表決。接近北京消息指，機會不大，原因是根據內地法規，<span style=\"color: red;\">常委會的草案一般應當經過三次會議審議，亦會作三十日徵詢意見，認為無論多急趕，都要跟程序走。<br />\n<br />\n即使跟程序，不代表不能特事特辦 。港區人大葉國謙預計，最快在月底加開特別會議，務必在七月通過法例。有資深人大形容，即使不是光速表決，都要盡快將國安法列入基本法附件三，而客觀效果之一，令國安法成為參選立法會必須宣誓擁護的基本法條文。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>希望蕭山今次能夠破燈，咁多消息來源都吻合，如果咁多燈嘅話，真係佩服到五體投地</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751ef2cc8bf36164d53f3cae67caceff89f6a2d7","tid":2071324,"uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T17:49:22.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334adf12635f9faeaaa471a0ec97a7ac3070e688","tid":2071324,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"要縮了"},{"pid":"fd5effea8fceba8ebaf320c963e08e8d6854ba18","tid":2071324,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9de2d3f0d77ac6078573840f6d0b07822d2f82","tid":2071324,"uid":315988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:20:40.000Z","msg":"快撚啲啦"},{"pid":"4cb5bf8e1d9c56fd6831a30ce17441a62773961b","tid":2071324,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199074911c38979bdc0cef477a826b44cec6282a","tid":2071324,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:27:07.000Z","msg":"燒山咪撚燈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c413c185ce4286f73d4da2616d0884a0bc4b27","tid":2071324,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:45:10.000Z","msg":"燒山又守護香港"},{"pid":"dbf2c940b7df0d779768d4736c6ab348e6ba93b0","tid":2071324,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T21:38:34.000Z","msg":"屌你我要攬炒呀，燒山你收聲得唔得呀？"},{"pid":"20b537666f58d7c23c86eecbf829a2c664036cf5","tid":2071324,"uid"